@startuml DeploymentDiagram

title Deployment Diagram: Dashboard Guru System

node "Client Device" {
  [Web Browser] <<device>>
  
  component "User Interface" {
    [HTML/CSS]
    [JavaScript]
    [Bootstrap/Sneat UI]
  }
}

node "Web Server" {
  component "Apache/Nginx" {
    [HTTP Server]
    [PHP-FPM]
  }
  
  component "Laravel Application" {
    [Routes]
    [Controllers]
    [Middleware]
    [Blade Engine]
  }
  
  component "Business Logic" {
    [Eloquent ORM]
    [Models]
    [Service Classes]
  }
  
  component "Libraries" {
    [DomPDF]
    [Laravel Breeze]
    [Laravel Boost]
  }
}

node "Database Server" {
  database "MySQL 8.0" {
    [dashboardguru_db]
  }
  
  folder "Tables" {
    [users]
    [serials]
    [classrooms]
    [students]
    [lessons]
    [exercises]
    [tasks]
    [exercise_points]
    [lesson_classroom]
    [exercise_classroom]
  }
}

node "File Storage" {
  folder "storage/app" {
    [uploaded_files]
    [student_attachments]
    [material_files]
  }
  
  folder "public/build" {
    [compiled_assets]
    [css_files]
    [js_files]
  }
}

node "External Services" <<cloud>> {
  [Composer Registry] <<external>>
  [NPM Registry] <<external>>
  [Packagist] <<external>>
}

' Connections
[Web Browser] --> [HTTP Server] : HTTPS/HTTP\nPort 80/443

[HTTP Server] --> [Routes] : Process Request
[Routes] --> [Middleware] : Apply Filters
[Middleware] --> [Controllers] : Route to Action
[Controllers] --> [Models] : Query Data
[Controllers] --> [DomPDF] : Generate PDF

[Eloquent ORM] --> [dashboardguru_db] : SQL Queries\nPort 3306
[Models] --> [Tables] : CRUD Operations

[Controllers] --> [Blade Engine] : Render Views
[Blade Engine] --> [Web Browser] : HTML Response

[Controllers] --> [uploaded_files] : Read/Write Files
[Blade Engine] --> [compiled_assets] : Load Assets

[Laravel Application] ..> [Composer Registry] : Install Packages
[User Interface] ..> [NPM Registry] : Install Dependencies

note right of [MySQL 8.0]
  Database Configuration:
  - Engine: InnoDB
  - Charset: utf8mb4
  - Collation: utf8mb4_unicode_ci
  - Foreign Keys: Enabled
  - Transactions: Enabled
end note

note right of [DomPDF]
  PDF Generation:
  - Landscape for class recap
  - Portrait for student detail
  - A4 paper size
  - UTF-8 encoding
end note

note left of [Web Browser]
  Supported Browsers:
  - Chrome/Edge (latest)
  - Firefox (latest)
  - Safari (latest)
  
  Features:
  - Responsive design
  - AJAX requests
  - File uploads
  - Modal dialogs
end note

@enduml
